## How to Use
1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/customer-segmentation.git
   ```
2. Install dependencies:
   ```bash
   pip install -r requirements.txt
   ```
3. Run Jupyter Notebook for analysis:
   ```bash
   jupyter notebook
   ```
4. Open `customer_segmentation.ipynb` and explore clustering techniques.

## Future Enhancements
- Implementing deep learning-based segmentation models.
- Integrating real-time customer segmentation with streaming data.
- Building an interactive segmentation tool for businesses.

